comments.body:
The function iterates over all transactions including finished ones from `GetBroadcastInfo()`, but only active (non-finished) transactions are abortable.
`to_stop.reserve(snapshot.size())` over-reserves since it is including finished transactions.

```suggestion
    for (const auto& entry : snapshot) {
      if (entry.final_state.has_value()) continue; // Skip already finished
      if (entry.tx->GetHash().ToUint256() == id || entry.tx->GetWitnessHash().ToUint256() == id) {
        to_stop.push_back(entry.tx);
      }
    }
```

